name: Makina - Y.A.I.A.L
description:
S1N3 invited me to collaborate on his collection “Young Amazon in a Landscape”, a commission for the Thyssen-Bornemisza National Museum from Madrid, Spain. They invited S1N3 to reimagine a classical painting. The original painting is “Young Knight in a Landscape” by Vittore Carpaccio.

This is the soundtrack for the collection.
